General.Name: Estrella Resources Ltd
General.Description: Estrella Resources Limited, together with its subsidiaries, explores for and develops nickel projects in Western Australia. It holds 100% interests in the Carr Boyd nickel project that includes three mining leases and six exploration licenses located near the city of Kalgoorlie-Boulder; and Spargoville nickel project situated near South-West of Kambalda. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Perth, Australia.
